  "system": {
    "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Athletic (+1):</strong> Halflings are nimble beings. They start with a d6 in Athletics instead of a d4. This increases their maximum Athletics to d12+1.</p></li><li><p><strong>Brave (+2):</strong> Halflings have the Brave Edge. Through cultural inheritance, they retain some amount of fearlessness from their Talentan origins.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lucky (+2):</strong> Halflings seemingly are able to find their way out of unideal situations. They draw one additional Benny per session. This stacks with Luck and Great Luck.</p></li><li><p><strong>Reduced Pace (−1):</strong> Halflings have short legs compared to human-sized ancestries. Decrease their Pace by 1 and their running die one die type.</p></li><li><p><strong>Size −1 (−1):</strong> Halflings are considered Size −1 and have −1 Toughness.</p></li><li><p><strong>Stealthy (+1):</strong> Halflings begin play with a d6 in Stealth. This increases their maximum Stealth to d12+1.</p></li></ul>",
